title: 1,900% Stock Gains and Hate Mail: Welcome to Quantum Investing
description: Rigetti Computing Inc. and D-Wave Quantum Inc. make products that so far have few real world applications. They’re burning through cash and aren’t expected to generate significant amounts of revenue for years. Despite all that, investors can’t get enough of them.

title: China to Resume Nexperia Chip Exports, Dutch PM Schoof Says
description: Dutch Prime Minister Dick Schoof said China has agreed to resume deliveries of Nexperia chips from plants in the country, signaling a potential breakthrough in a clash that risked disrupting global auto production.

title: Nvidia CEO Asks TSMC for More Wafers to Meet Strong AI Demand
description: Nvidia Corp. Chief Executive Officer Jensen Huang said he had asked Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co. for more chip supplies as artificial intelligence demand remains strong.
